## 🔧 代码实现规范

### 1. Widget 实现

```dart
// ✅ 正确示例
class ProfileHeader extends StatelessWidget {
  const ProfileHeader({
    Key? key,
    required this.user,
  }) : super(key: key);

  final User user;

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Container(
      padding: EdgeInsets.all(
        AppSpacing.semantic[DesignSemanticConstants.container]?[DesignSemanticConstants.md] ?? AppSpacing.containerMd,
      ),
      decoration: BoxDecoration(
        color: AppColors.light.backgroundPrimary,
        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(AppSpacing.borderRadius),
      ),
      child: Row(
        children: [
          CircleAvatar(
            radius: AppSpacing.avatarSize / 2,
            backgroundImage: NetworkImage(user.avatarUrl),
          ),
          SizedBox(width: AppSpacing.md),
          Expanded(
            child: Column(
              crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
              children: [
                Text(
                  user.name,
                  style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.titleMedium,
                ),
                SizedBox(height: AppSpacing.xs),
                Text(
                  user.bio,
                  style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.bodySmall,
                ),
              ],
            ),
          ),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

### 2. 状态管理

```dart
// ✅ 正确示例
class ProfileState {
  final bool isLoading;
  final User? user;
  final String? error;
  
  const ProfileState({
    required this.isLoading,
    this.user,
    this.error,
  });
  
  ProfileState copyWith({
    bool? isLoading,
    User? user,
    String? error,
  }) {
    return ProfileState(
      isLoading: isLoading ?? this.isLoading,
      user: user ?? this.user,
      error: error ?? this.error,
    );
  }
}

class ProfileNotifier extends StateNotifier<ProfileState> {
  final ProfileService _service;
  
  ProfileNotifier(this._service) : super(const ProfileState(isLoading: false));
  
  Future<void> loadProfile(String userId) async {
    try {
      state = state.copyWith(isLoading: true, error: null);
      final user = await _service.getProfile(userId);
      state = state.copyWith(isLoading: false, user: user);
    } catch (e) {
      state = state.copyWith(isLoading: false, error: e.toString());
    }
  }
}
```

### 3. 错误处理

```dart
// ✅ 正确示例
Future<List<Post>> getPosts({int page = 1}) async {
  try {
    final response = await _httpClient.get('/posts?page=$page');
    if (response.statusCode == 200) {
      final data = json.decode(response.body);
      return (data['posts'] as List)
          .map((json) => Post.fromJson(json))
          .toList();
    } else {
      throw NetworkException('Failed to load posts: ${response.statusCode}');
    }
  } on SocketException {
    throw NetworkException('No internet connection');
  } on TimeoutException {
    throw NetworkException('Request timeout');
  } on FormatException {
    throw NetworkException('Invalid response format');
  } catch (e) {
    if (e is AppException) {
      rethrow;
    }
    throw NetworkException('Unexpected error: $e');
  }
}
```

## 📋 检查清单

在提交代码前，必须检查：

- [ ] 所有颜色都使用语义标签（AppColors.*）
- [ ] 所有间距都使用语义标签（AppSpacing.*）
- [ ] 所有文本都使用常量（UITextConstants.*）
- [ ] 所有类型都使用常量（ContentTypeConstants.*）
- [ ] 语义间距使用空值安全操作符（?.）
- [ ] 没有硬编码颜色值（Color(0x...）
- [ ] 没有硬编码间距（EdgeInsets.all(16)）
- [ ] 没有魔鬼数字（48.h, 24.sp）
- [ ] 所有异步操作都有错误处理
- [ ] 运行 `flutter analyze` 无错误

## 🔍 快速检查命令

```bash
# 检查硬编码颜色
grep -r "Color(0x" lib/ | grep -v "AppColors"

# 检查硬编码间距
grep -r "EdgeInsets\.all(" lib/ | grep -v "AppSpacing"

# 检查硬编码文本
grep -r "'[^']*'" lib/ | grep -v "UITextConstants\|ContentTypeConstants\|DesignSemanticConstants"

# 运行静态分析
flutter analyze
```

